room_title: Escape room "The Tiki Lounge" by Puzzles in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description:
While on vacation on the Island of POOZLES, you heard about the local legend of the 5 Golden Squirrels. Upon learning they have never been found, you and your group have made it your mission to spend the rest of your vacation locating these squirrels. 
Can you decipher the clues? Solve the riddles and become legends!
